        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>On some bus models the bottom of the battery box may deform, or begin to separate from the sides
                    of the box, under the weight of the vehicle's batteries (Figure 1). A field kit that contains two
                    corner supports and fasteners, for reinforcement of the battery box, is now available to address
                    this issue.
                </para>
                <figure id="f0647031" figsize="pg-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/G0647031.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="514px"
                             scalefitheight="248px"/>
                    <caption>Figure 1. Battery Box Before and After Repair (Prior to Refinishing)</caption>
                </figure>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
